message: We've been in business for 8 years. We cover all of South Florida - Miami-Dade, Broward, and Palm Beach counties. We typically work within a 50-mile radius. Our website is turfgrassartificialsolutions.com. We do residential lawns, commercial properties, playgrounds, sports fields, and putting greens.
